testsuite-h100-ecoc-demo (1.4) stable; urgency=medium

  * Added ./test-odl-install script that install and configures OpenDaylight to mount
    the 3 nodes
  * Added ./test-odl-clear-traffic-generators that deletes/stops all traffic generators
    in the network using OpenDaylight northbound RESTCONF interface instead of direct
    connection to the nodes

